# Minnesota Hiking
![](../../zresources/img/MNhiking.jpg){fig-align="center"}

Kim and I often go to Minnesota for long weekend vacations. We primarily hike and eat good food and drink craft beer on these trips. Below are some of our hikes.







- **Duluth Area**
  - [Ely's Peak via Short Line Trail](MN ElyPeak ShortLine.html)
  - [Waabizheshikana Trail Loop](MN Waabizheshikana.html)

- **North Shore**
  - [Fantasia Overlook (Silver Bay)](MN Fantasia.html)
  - [High and Middle Falls (Grand Portage SP)](MN Grand Portage.html)
  - [Kadunce River trail](MN Kadunce.html)
  - [Split Rock River](MN Split Rock River.html)
  - [Temperance River loop](MN Temperance Loop.html)
  - [Tettegouche SP and Shovel Point](MN Tettegouche Shovel Point.html)
